p: \bWell, well, well!
\bNow... what do we got here?
\bA challenger! We haven't had one of those in a while, no sir.
\bThe name's Eduard. I'm an Elite Four member, as you could probably tell.
\bSand...
\bIt's coarse, and it gets everywhere, but I love it all the same.
\bLet's get going. You're going to get shut down so hard you won't even know what hit you.
pbTrainerIntro(:ELITEFOUR_Darude)
$PokemonGlobal.nextBattleBack="E4Desert"
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ELITEFOUR_Darude,"Eduard","Whoa! Very nicely done.",false,0)
for poke in $Trainer.party
if poke.hp==0
$game_variables[170] = pbGet(170) - 1
end
end
\bWell... not bad. Not bad at all.
\bYou've got spirit, kid. You could go far.
\bThe doors to our Champion should open for you, now.
\bBest of luck... you'll definitely need it.

\bBest of luck... you'll definitely need it.
pbTrainerEnd
